## Food Delivery App

A modern full-stack food delivery platform built with React, Spring-Boot, Node.js and MySQL

# Features
- JWT Authentication
- Browse restaurants & menus
- Add to cart & checkout
- Stripe test payments
- Real-time order tracking 
- Google Maps integration
- Email notifications
- Admin dashboard


# Tech Stack
- Frontend: React + Tailwind + Axios
- Backend (Java): SpringBoot 3 (Orders, Users, Restaurants)
- Backend (Node): Express.js (Payments, Maps, Notifications)
- Databases: MySQL
- Integrations: Stripe API, Google Maps API
- Deployment: Docker, Vercel (frontend), Render/Fly (backends), Railway (MySQL)


# QuickStart
'''bash
# Run all services
docker-compose up --build